The paper proposes a hardware platform for implementing neural networks and neuromorphic computing, which falls under the category of "Emerging Technologies" (cs.ET). The platform combines semiconductor and superconductor technologies, which could also fall under "Neural and Evolutionary Computing" (cs.NE) and "Optical Computing" (cs.OC). The paper also discusses the use of photonics and waveguides, which could be relevant to "Signal Processing" (cs.SP). Finally, the paper discusses the potential for scaling to systems with massive interconnectivity and complexity, which could fall under "Systems and Control" (cs.SY).
